[12/02/2018 19:41:00] <font color="#00ffff">John y Shannon Le Sayla</font>
[12/02/2018 19:41:00] <font color="#00ffff">son dos peces gordos</font>
[12/02/2018 19:41:03] <font color="#00ffff">del sector del cultivo de ostras.</font>
